MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: apps/client/src/(shells/[^/]+/hooks/.+\.ts|store/useGameStore\.ts)$
MATCH_CONTENT: (stances|responses|submitted|decisions|votes|confessions|answers|guesses|choices|submissions|participated|completedPhases)
ADVISORY: |
  Cartridge SYNC projections in `apps/game-server/src/projections.ts` strip
  sensitive fields by phase. Before reading a cartridge field client-side,
  verify it exists in the projection for the relevant phase:

  - CONFESSION: `confessions` stripped during COLLECTING/VOTING; `votes` only during VOTING
  - GUESS_WHO: `answers` stripped during ANSWERING; `guesses` stripped during GUESSING
  - DILEMMA: `decisions` stripped during COLLECTING; `submitted` is the pre-REVEAL signal
  - WOULD_YOU_RATHER: uses `choices`, NOT `stances`/`responses`
  - HOT_TAKE / PLAYER_PICK / PREDICTION: use `stances` / `responses`

  Grep `apps/game-server/src/machines/cartridges/` for machine shape, then
  `apps/game-server/src/projections.ts` for projected shape BEFORE proposing
  a client-side read. Don't invent fields like `submissions` that exist in
  no machine.
